Anytime Fitness Eastwood Centre is a great little gym tucked in a quiet neighbourhood, just opposite Bedok Corner. It is fully equipped with machines for all muscle groups, and the space is clean and well-maintained.

I usually come in around 6am when it is peaceful, or around 6pm where it is slightly busier but still filled with like-minded people who respect gym etiquette. The atmosphere is always positive.

Special mention to the staff,  Anuar, Asri, and Amirul who are super friendly and helpful. They are always ready to guide newcomers and make everyone feel welcome. Their presence really lifts the vibe of the place.

Highly recommend this branch if you are looking for a no-frills, cosy gym with good people and good energy.
